Who 

Groups sharing tracking their reading progress - ie Bookclubs, students in a classroom reading the same text

Individual book readers track their collection and reading progress.

What can the web app  do
Bookshelf - Books where one can share what they are reading and how much progress they have made
Join reading groups with set times for progressing through the group
Map that shows local independent bookstores in the area

Framework: Bulma  

Backend AirTable
Store user accounts
Store books - Associated ratings
APIs
Google Maps API to show bookstore
Open Books API to get information about books
